                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-red-200 mb-8">
                        <h4 class="font-extrabold text-red-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock text-jambo-red"></i> Raw Payment Data (Read-Only Warning)</h4>
